# RDF Changelog

## 2.0.0 (unreleased)

### Phase 2 — CC Adapter + State Helper + CLI + GitHub
[New] bin/rdf CLI dispatcher — Sigforge sf pattern with lazy-sourced subcommands
[New] lib/rdf_common.sh — shared init, version, path helpers, require guards
[New] rdf generate claude-code — canonical + metadata -> CC output with YAML frontmatter
[New] rdf sync — reverse flow strips frontmatter, detects drift, supports --dry-run
[New] rdf state — deterministic project state JSON in <1s (no LLM)
[New] rdf github — setup, sync-labels, ecosystem-init, ecosystem-add
[New] adapters/claude-code/agent-meta.json — CC frontmatter for all 12 agents
[New] adapters/claude-code/hooks/hooks.json — hook event definitions
[New] .claude-plugin/plugin.json — CC plugin manifest
[Change] /root/.claude/{commands,agents,scripts} now symlinked to adapter output
[Fix] Version detection handles rfxn patterns (V=, VER=, VERSION=, *_version=)
[Fix] grep -c fallback avoids doubled output (anti-pattern #29)
[Remove] overwatch-hook.sh reference from settings.json SubagentStop hooks

### Phase 1 — Canonical Migration + Naming Overhaul
[New] Canonical-first architecture — tool-agnostic storage
[New] {domain}-{role} naming convention for all agents/commands
[New] Self-verification gates in QA and Sentinel agents
[New] Scope confirmation protocol in EM/mgr command
[New] sec-eng agent and command
[New] mgr agent definition (for Agent Teams delegate mode)
[Change] workforce/ renamed to rdf/
[Change] RDF is authoritative — /root/.claude/ is deployment target, not source
[Change] All agent/command cross-references updated for new naming
[Remove] overwatch-hook.sh (Overwatch project dead)
[Remove] sync.sh and install.sh (replaced by rdf generate + rdf sync)

## 1.0.1
Documentation accuracy pass. See git log for details.

## 1.0.0
Initial release. Workforce reference framework.
